      "content": "that makes sense. i'll check if remove_oldest is actually calling delete. \n\nif it turns out the leak isn't in that specific function, how do i narrow it down if the codebase is massive? i'm looking for something that's just creeping up in the background without crashing the system immediately. it feels like it's hiding in some corner of the logic i haven't looked at yet.",
